description: First loves are never easy, and for Julian Bell and Theo Brady, things are complicated by the fact that Theo is afraid of publicly outing himself to his parents, so as much as it pains Julian to have to part ways, he doesn't want to live a lie. Theo knows all of this, which is why he's come to Julian to try and win him back, and though he knows Julian will be skeptical, Theo has a secret to share with Julian that he thinks just might change his mind once and for all. But this is one secret Julian is gonna need to see for himself before he believes. Luckily, Theo has every intention of showing Julian exactly what he wants to see. Enjoy!
title: Love Wins
